issue.title: Problem installing nloptr, a dependency for sesame

repository.name: xqtl-pipeline
repository.description: Molecular QTL data analysis pipeline developed for ADSP functional genomic xQTL consortium

issue.body:
While installing nloptr using r version 4.1.3 (as dependency requirement for sesame is R>=4.10) and the newest biocmanager version, following error occurs:

```
/mnt/mfs/cluster/bin/R-4.1.3/etc/Makeconf:177: recipe for target 'test-C-API.o' failed
make: *** [test-C-API.o] Error 1
ERROR: compilation failed for package 'nloptr'
* removing '/mnt/mfs/hgrcgrid/homes/hs3163/R/x86_64-pc-linux-gnu-library/4.1/nloptr'

The downloaded source packages are in
        '/tmp/RtmpYeEpIC/downloaded_packages'
Installation paths not writeable, unable to update packages
  path: /mnt/mfs/cluster/bin/R-4.1.3/library
  packages:
    MASS, Matrix, cluster, mgcv, nlme, survival
Warning message:
In install.packages(...) :
  installation of package 'nloptr' had non-zero exit status
```

with one error happened before:

```
mv: cannot move 'nlopt/lib' to a subdirectory of itself, 'nlopt/lib/lib'
configure: creating ./config.status
config.status: creating src/Makevars
```

and various error during the invocation of `test-C-API.o`:
```
In file included from /mnt/mfs/hgrcgrid/homes/hs3163/R/x86_64-pc-linux-gnu-library/4.1/testthat/include/testthat/testthat.h:65:0,
                 from /mnt/mfs/hgrcgrid/homes/hs3163/R/x86_64-pc-linux-gnu-library/4.1/testthat/include/testthat.h:1,
                 from test-C-API.cpp:12:
test-C-API.cpp: In function 'void ____C_A_T_C_H____T_E_S_T____0()':
test-C-API.cpp:107:35: error: call of overloaded 'abs(__gnu_cxx::__alloc_traits<std::allocator<double> >::value_type)' is ambiguous
     expect_true(abs(res[0] - 1./ 3) < 1.0e-4);
                                   ^
test-C-API.cpp:107:5: note: in expansion of macro 'expect_true'
     expect_true(abs(res[0] - 1./ 3) < 1.0e-4);
```
